    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2130300/extras/054c4cd202db45f5d2ed3a91c63bda94.avif?t=1746589459\" width=613 height=367 /></span><br>Eclipse: Shine of Dawn 是一款具有奇幻 RPG 美学的游戏，结合了最佳的故事讲述和砍杀元素、独特的角色、令人难忘的敌人以及令人愉悦的环境中的身临其境的谜题，无论是思考、欣赏还是击败部落 怪物。 随着故事的进展，解锁新的武器、能力和情感，以完全史诗般的方式呈现独特的时刻。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2130300/extras/b0a8f110f027c2048e41bd4cd3865d4c.poster.avif?t=1746589459\" width=613 height=287 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2130300/extras/b0a8f110f027c2048e41bd4cd3865d4c.webm?t=1746589459\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2130300/extras/0d52a9dfd523ade2d9a03a4bc57d4d22.avif?t=1746589459\" width=613 height=273 /></span><br>- 原创世界建筑，拥有自己的神话、地区和生物。<br>- 不同武器之间交替的组合系统。<br>- 通过基于任务的系统进行武器进化。<br>- 可扩展的宇宙。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2130300/extras/38ff8fe2585ded790238edd40e4dc8a4.poster.avif?t=1746589459\" width=613 height=287 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2130300/extras/38ff8fe2585ded790238edd40e4dc8a4.webm?t=1746589459\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2130300/extras/d77ed6580ce8134bd2ae1ae40d56f18c.webp?t=1746589459\" width=613 height=50 /></span><br>跟随卢克踏上权力崛起之旅，完成他的使命。 面对尼洛王子被绑架，卢克面临着一个不可避免的境地，他必须在一路上与对手对抗，寻求最大限度地提升自己的能力，以便在巅峰时能够对抗黑暗的气势——黑暗一者。 。 与英雄一起踏上这段充满神秘、行动和强烈情感的奇妙旅程。 增强传奇之剑Suncatcher和神话武器，掌握每一种可用的能力来摧毁巨大的邪恶。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2130300/extras/e629b5c3669c2c16e763a8e608bdafd8.poster.avif?t=1746589459\" width=613 height=287 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2130300/extras/e629b5c3669c2c16e763a8e608bdafd8.webm?t=1746589459\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2130300/extras/e607205130dac18c94a5b1bcb536e98b.webp?t=1746589459\" width=613 height=50 /></span><br>每个人在旅途中都追求更高的目标，当两条相反的道路交叉时，对抗就不可避免。 然而，每一次冲突，无论大小，都会点燃成就的光芒。 冲突中结下羁绊，观点发生变化，熊熊燃烧的火焰可以照亮每个人旅程的新愿景。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2130300/extras/172f34df0de97acd2a429062279573c5.poster.avif?t=1746589459\" width=613 height=287 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2130300/extras/172f34df0de97acd2a429062279573c5.webm?t=1746589459\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2130300/extras/01bfe7c536321cfafa6299e34d24b0b3.webp?t=1746589459\" width=613 height=50 /></span><br>了解传奇武器在 Eclipse 宇宙中的协同作用如何。 了解它们的原始元素如何相互作用并产生奇妙的效果。 让组合成为你最强大的武器，并被如此多的可能性所吸引。",
